{"tid":1524294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布黨鐵向全香港人宣戰","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:16:59.000Z","uid":168795,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f3e43cbaed523670d844e3ba14c99b516e191a","tid":1524294,"uid":168795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"黨鐵為黑警服務 不是服務香港人 多次協助恐襲發生<br />\n無論是來自白衣人定係黑警既恐襲都係有黨鐵全力協助<br />\n最近仲幫助黑警去封站<br />\n香港人唔係仲忍氣吞聲掛<br />\n香港人要做d野 <br />\n比黨鐵知道你地老闆係邊個 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a33c92cce85ff176f1a37f742e3acd2fc55003","tid":1524294,"uid":168795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c91c549495f549a5d090e13739eb71310d691fc","tid":1524294,"uid":143699,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n完整示範片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70iZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=3c239574\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"3d7d7aece47e92bdb77cd3fd11e7dc09497d6962","tid":1524294,"uid":169023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"聽日1:00機場見<br />\n出post啊"},{"pid":"cde50bd693c874efb190d377682e8acaf7fb8181","tid":1524294,"uid":17502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"而家唔係要跳閘，係要整爛曬所有閘"},{"pid":"2ff6495872c0115d1cff142a43be2122cb086f8b","tid":1524294,"uid":37968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"擺搭啦"},{"pid":"6b6ef9f90f0b32f527c914464496eebf31955b89","tid":1524294,"uid":17714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e23423c5efa884370cc4948ba7ca967bc325d2fa","tid":1524294,"uid":168795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cde50bd693c874efb190d377682e8acaf7fb8181","tid":1524