41751317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n@thestandnews <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47df1d91ecc1d706923ed519f0859fdc8e847786","tid":1524294,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非出動嘅時候到了 你唔係忍到今日手足為你犧牲呀?"},{"pid":"ab30c5afc9e8e255887d94e7ad85bd7b9fb3f326","tid":1524294,"uid":208092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"拆閘門 拆閘機 打玻璃"},{"pid":"768e199712d95537283d758570c29a5cf16b25e7","tid":1524294,"uid":49687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:50:50.000Z","msg":"831 香港警察策謀恐襲"},{"pid":"e73af430f0f7040ccb62e6072711e03ed32f6f1c","tid":1524294,"uid":168795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T23:53:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63be3877c134495cb21f49c8f1e6234012e1920c","tid":1524294,"uid":168795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cd22fd15e03a6579372957125c8c47c71868fee","tid":1524294,"uid":309935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T00:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7acb0ad67ccd0269c2ebf2c2061c51e53fdbc7b","tid":1524294,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c91c549495f549a5d090e13739eb71310d691fc","tid":1524294,"uid":143699,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一